{"tid":344274,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得去台灣旅行根本係折磨？","createTime":"2017-08-02T07:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T00:30:42.000Z","uid":131753,"like":62,"dislike":135,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e05ff57821b9538f055b6538565e9fee45b875b4","tid":344274,"uid":131753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:24:45.000Z","msg":"D人成撚日神化台灣 話咩台灣好撚正 一年最少去一次咁 住又舒適 食野又正 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我屌你地老味啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台灣其實根本就同大陸地方冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去過一次真係咪撚再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔撚係特別平 我寧願去少兩次台灣都要去轉日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偏偏仲要大撚把人吹到移民首選台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總括黎講 我會比0.25/10分 個0.25分係比食物算尚可接受 <br />\n<br />\n認同樓主 台灣根本垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你咩傻閪 台灣咁撚正都屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25370be0a8beaf044341441eb8afdcdd007e2ba","tid":344274,"uid":100016,"like":35,"dislike":7,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"有人鐘意有人唔鐘意，投黎有乜意義，無聊"},{"pid":"19760d43b8e7df435afceb2192c501984b9dac26","tid":344274,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人鐘意有人唔鐘意，投黎有乜意義，無聊</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c014a9f84d58fd23396ae92d61022591ef3f4a76","tid":344274,"uid":33668,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人鐘意有人唔鐘意，投黎有乜意義，無聊</blockquote><br />\n網上認同感好重要駕"},{"pid":"5a7aeced2ab82afe25ae8f3f894b0062161279c5","tid":344274,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:32:21.000Z",